BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_314167736@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260518T015405Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260518T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260518T200000
SUMMARY:Conscious Conversations & Embodied Listening  
DESCRIPTION:Iama Embodied Community\nThis is a spiritual community that ho
 nors the body’s wisdom and lived experience. Whether you’re healing fr
 om religious trauma\, deconstructing beliefs\, exploring spirituality\, or
  just want to be with other conscious persons\, this space is for you.\n\n
 Expect conscious conversations\, meditation\, breathwork\, sound healing\,
  and other somatic practices to help reconnect with ourselves and each oth
 er.\n\nwe share a potluck dinner every last Monday of the month.\n\n📅 *
 *Date & Time**: Mondays 6-8 PM\n📍 **Location**: 727 T St. Sacramento\, 
 Ca\, 95811\n💜 **All our events are free\, donations supported.**\n✨ *
 *No prior experience or spiritual beliefs necessary.**\n📩 **RSVP/ Quest
 ions? Reach out at** embody.iama@gmail.com\n🔗 **Follow us on Instagram:
 ** [@embody.iama](https://www.instagram.com/embody.iama)\n\nPS: we meet in
  the social hall of Parkview Presbyterian Church. Please find us through t
 he back entrance\, the brown gate on Solons alley. You may park in the bac
 k\, move the orange post to park and please return it when you leave.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindful-embodied-spirituality/events/
 314167736/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260407T181427Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260407T181427Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_314710330@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260518T015405Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260519T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260519T110000
SUMMARY:Gentle yoga
DESCRIPTION:Iama Embodied Community\nThis is a slow and mindful practice t
 hat emphasizes deep breathing\, body awareness\, and nervous system regula
 tion. This class is accessible to all abilities\, providing a supportive a
 nd trauma-informed space to reconnect with the body.\n\nSessions alternate
  between floor yoga and chair yoga (on the 2nd and 4th Tuesday). Stay a bi
 t longer on the last Tuesday of the month and join us for coffee or tea af
 terward!\n\nLike all our events\, this class is free\, donations are welco
 me.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindful-embodied-spirituality/events/
 314710330/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260511T040044Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260511T040044Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313017921@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260518T015405Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260521T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260521T191000
SUMMARY:Free Yoga Practice
DESCRIPTION:Iama Embodied Community\n🌀 **Move with intention. Connect w
 ith your body. Celebrate community.**\n\nJoin us every **Thursday at 6 PM*
 * for an embodied yoga practice designed to help you release tension\, gro
 und yourself\, and cultivate presence. This is a trauma-informed\, all-lev
 els class\, no prior yoga experience needed. Expect a Hatha-Vinyasa flow\,
  breathwork\, and a space to listen to your body’s wisdom.\n\n🌿 **Eve
 ry last Thursday of the month\, stay after class for a community potluck d
 inner!**\n\n📍 **Location**: 727 T St. Sacramento CA 95811\n✨ **All ou
 r events are free. Donations are welcome.**\n📩 **Questions? Reach out a
 t** embody.iama@gmail.com\n🔗 **Follow us on Instagram:** [@embody.iama]
 (https://www.instagram.com/embody.iama)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindful-embodied-spirituality/events/
 313017921/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260123T082354Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260123T082354Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
